{"tid":2510200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賭爛樓上漏水不處理　他連開5年「震樓神器」！全社區住戶都崩潰了","createTime":"2021-04-30T03:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T04:56:20.000Z","uid":117088,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"69af3fc0b6fc2d96fafe7d23f3a7b18932323884","tid":2510200,"uid":117088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"住戶不滿樓上鄰居的陽台水管老化不處理，導致漏水到自己家中，火大買震樓神器開24小時連開5年，讓全社區的住戶都快瘋了。<br />\n據《新民晚報》報導，中國上海浦東新區上南花城社區的住戶，家裡都有耳塞，因為某棟502室住戶與樓上602室發生爭執，一怒之下使用了震樓器，一震就是五年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/dOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png&h=04b0283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社區居民指出，白天因為有白噪音，所以還能擋住一些噪音，但是到了晚上，震樓神器的聲音變得異常清晰，但最厲害的是一種低頻震動，「這個功能一開，整棟樓都在抖，震得人腦殼嗡嗡響」，這兩種攻擊都是24小時不間斷進行，已經持續了整5年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/SmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png&h=da8668b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n說起和樓下的恩怨，602室的王女士說，多年前和樓下的502是好朋友，2016年時她們家陽台的水管老化漏水影響到了樓下，因為沒有好好溝通，樓下就開始使用震樓神器攻擊，整個社區的人都精神萎靡，睡眠不好。<br />\n究竟502住戶的訴求是什麼？有住戶指出，502的訴求就是想讓602搬走。602王女士說她願意投降，「只要他們(502)願意開門溝通，我馬上就下樓賠禮道歉，或是其他什麼解決方式，都可以商量，只要停止震樓什麼都好說。」王女士說，至今還記得和樓下鄰居相處甚歡的時光，現在她每天睡在客廳的席夢思上都會思考，事情為什麼會變成這樣？（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"f5c643b34880fdc696e1e4eae2fc50391bc0fc35","tid":2510200,"uid":289946,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"有錢買席夢思都唔整翻條喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdf12b924724532d17fa89d8472b9e420cb00b0","tid":2510200,"uid":52824,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:48:05.000Z","msg":"震足5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a87c50b444151bd53b4a19dfac9a1120d31e58","tid":2510200,"uid":916,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"quote":{"pid":"69af3fc0b6fc2d96fafe7d23f3a7b18932323884","tid":2510200,"uid":117088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"住戶不滿樓上鄰居的陽台水管老化不處理，導致漏水到自己家中，火大買震樓神器開24小時連開5年，讓全社區的住戶都快瘋了。<br />\n據《新民晚報》報導，中國上海浦東新區上南花城社區的住戶，家裡都有耳塞，因為某棟502室住戶與樓上602室發生爭執，一怒之下使用了震樓器，一震就是五年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/dOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png&h=04b0283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社區居民指出，白天因為有白噪音，所以還能擋住一些噪音，但是到了晚上，震樓神器的聲音變得異常清晰，但最厲害的是一種低頻震動，「這個功能一開，整棟樓都在抖，震得人腦殼嗡嗡響」，這兩種攻擊都是24小時不間斷進行，已經持續了整5年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/SmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png&h=da8668b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\