03:59:24.000Z","msg":"現在她每天睡在客廳的席夢思上都會思考，事情為什麼會變成這樣？（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪新聞賣植入式廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3654706b552326c6345863d0a038f9fc6848ea64","tid":2510200,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f0395c20cbb40cbe44b260cd3c5c73bf8125fe2","tid":2510200,"uid":105798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"現在她每天睡在客廳的<span class=\"red\">席夢思</span>上都會思考<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"席夢思，乜撚野事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01041d2d4ca79393f2a2fc068ba46c1718797a4f","tid":2510200,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69af3fc0b6fc2d96fafe7d23f3a7b18932323884","tid":2510200,"uid":117088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"住戶不滿樓上鄰居的陽台水管老化不處理，導致漏水到自己家中，火大買震樓神器開24小時連開5年，讓全社區的住戶都快瘋了。<br />\n據《新民晚報》報導，中國上海浦東新區上南花城社區的住戶，家裡都有耳塞，因為某棟502室住戶與樓上602室發生爭執，一怒之下使用了震樓器，一震就是五年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/dOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png&h=04b0283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社區居民指出，白天因為有白噪音，所以還能擋住一些噪音，但是到了晚上，震樓神器的聲音變得異常清晰，但最厲害的是一種低頻震動，「這個功能一開，整棟樓都在抖，震得人腦殼嗡嗡響」，這兩種攻擊都是24小時不間斷進行，已經持續了整5年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/SmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png&h=da8668b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n說起和樓下的恩怨，602室的王女士說，多年前和樓下的502是好朋友，2016年時她們家陽台的水管老化漏水影響到了樓下，因為沒有好好溝通，樓下就開始使用震樓神器攻擊，整個社區的人都精神萎靡，睡眠不好。<br />\n究竟502住戶的訴求是什麼？有住戶指出，502的訴求就是想讓602搬走。602王女士說她願意投降，「只要他們(502)願意開門溝通，我馬上就下樓賠禮道歉，或是其他什麼解決方式，都可以商量，只要停止震樓什麼都好說。」王女士說，至今還記得和樓下鄰居相處甚歡的時光，現在她每天睡在客廳的席夢思上都會思考，事情為什麼會變成這樣？（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"大陸都有晴報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d23f7f30e79ca831a848568e8a01674e8d33ca","tid":2510200,"uid":57597,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"支那新聞關我哋咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae125ec957fdf561c045dc592cb6fdf3ffc2040","tid":2510200,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8892546e83535bb8e0c5412bbcadfa4dea80f33c","tid":25102