ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"公安搞鄰里糾紛又無政績，又唔可以立亂爆門<br />\n緊係理得你慢慢嘈飽佢"},{"pid":"0fb87dae8d66d40e8367ce4fbb19ca5d2a9d3646","tid":2510200,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"邊到買 想由40樓震到落一樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a4fd23849e3253dbbbfe1d9c15dc4bf6bbe6e8","tid":2510200,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42aecdcc2c41b476fd5152eaf5b1df47ae57c3ca","tid":2510200,"uid":33522,"like":123,"dislike":0,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"王女士說，至今還記得和樓下鄰居相處甚歡的時光，現在她每天睡在客廳的席夢思上都會思考，事情為什麼會變成這樣？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />漏水唔整而家係咪扮無知 好撚嘔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"呢啲人真係好乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37b4b5fe2514a01c350614f6eeb2841fccc50c2","tid":2510200,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69af3fc0b6fc2d96fafe7d23f3a7b18932323884","tid":2510200,"uid":117088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"住戶不滿樓上鄰居的陽台水管老化不處理，導致漏水到自己家中，火大買震樓神器開24小時連開5年，讓全社區的住戶都快瘋了。<br />\n據《新民晚報》報導，中國上海浦東新區上南花城社區的住戶，家裡都有耳塞，因為某棟502室住戶與樓上602室發生爭執，一怒之下使用了震樓器，一震就是五年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/dOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png&h=04b0283f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社區居民指出，白天因為有白噪音，所以還能擋住一些噪音，但是到了晚上，震樓神器的聲音變得異常清晰，但最厲害的是一種低頻震動，「這個功能一開，整棟樓都在抖，震得人腦殼嗡嗡響」，這兩種攻擊都是24小時不間斷進行，已經持續了整5年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/SmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSmkM5oqTmPPgeR6iLDQrqepDi2A%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASLMZB6ZVRCDXODZWYEHKYXIU4.png&h=da8668b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n說起和樓下的恩怨，602室的王女士說，多年前和樓下的502是好朋友，2016年時她們家陽台的水管老化漏水影響到了樓下，因為沒有好好溝通，樓下就開始使用震樓神器攻擊，整個社區的人都精神萎靡，睡眠不好。<br />\n究竟502住戶的訴求是什麼？有住戶指出，502的訴求就是想讓602搬走。602王女士說她願意投降，「只要他們(502)願意開門溝通，我馬上就下樓賠禮道歉，或是其他什麼解決方式，都可以商量，只要停止震樓什麼都好說。」王女士說，至今還記得和樓下鄰居相處甚歡的時光，現在她每天睡在客廳的席夢思上都會思考，事情為什麼會變成這樣？（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"香港有冇啲咁嘅閪住戶"},{"pid":"f66a45531bade69ecee75c68684cf71cd42252ab","tid":2510200,"uid":278972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ubBuEkH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FubBuEkH.gif&h=33ff5ab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"303528648dc7b3368116db463e7400b71792e557","tid":2510200,"uid":265338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69af3fc0b6fc2d96fafe7d23f3a7b18932323884","tid":2510200,"uid":117088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"住戶不滿樓上鄰居的陽台水管老化不處理，導致漏水到自己家中，火大買震樓神器開24小時連開5年，讓全社區的住戶都快瘋了。<br />\n據《新民晚報》報導，中國上海浦東新區上南花城社區的住戶，家裡都有耳塞，因為某棟502室住戶與樓上602室發生爭執，一怒之下使用了震樓器，一震就是五年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/dOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY=/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdOdWEm5Cd4xYc70b7CgxGPOWXoY%3D%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBZAQXUOIBZFONDDSQVCJRI355Y.png&h=04b0283f&s={S